    {
      "id": "skill-extract-root",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "🪶 Skill: extract-subgraph (Normative)",
      "position": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "width": 860,
      "height": 340,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Skill: extract-subgraph\n\n**Category:** Structural Skill\n\nLift a subset of a graph into a new portable graph without losing meaning, identity, or closure.\n\nExtraction is controlled graph birth.\n\nThis graph is the contract.",
